name: core::<iter::adapters::map::Map<I, F> as iter::traits::double_ended::DoubleEndedIterator>::try_rfold
src:
fn try_rfold<Acc, G, R>(&mut self, init: Acc, g: G) -> R
    where
        Self: Sized,
        G: FnMut(Acc, Self::Item) -> R,
        R: Try<Output = Acc>,
    {
        self.iter.try_rfold(init, map_try_fold(&mut self.f, g))
    }
